==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Glorification
<hw>Glo`ri*fi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>glorificatio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>glorification</ets>. See
<er>Glorify</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of glorifying or of
giving glory to.</def> <rj><au>Jer. Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of being glorifed; <as>as, the
<ex>glorification</ex> of Christ after his resurrection</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>glorified</ent>⟦br⟧
